flowRoot.flowPara: Debian is a free computer operating system developed by a community of volunteers all across the world. Which includes thousands of software packages released for free, easily accessible using the repositories. Debian is focused on stability and security, while being dedicated to the Debian Social Contract and Free Software.
Debian Buster is the 10th major release, yours to use and enjoy.
